						"key": "kosso",
						"displayName": "kosso",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/London"
					},
					"body": "Also, if anyone does have an idea on how this might be done, I do build my own Ti SDKs at this end, so am willing to modify and test out any objectiveC code to test it ;) ",
					"updateAuthor": {
