						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "kosso -\r\n\r\nThis ticket has only just now come to my attention. Because this is an HIG violation, we'll be trying to schedule it this week or next, but with the 1.8.0.1 release upcoming, there are no guarantees on a fix timeframe.\r\n\r\nOriginally it was triaged and tagged for inclusion in 1.9.0, so it's unlikely to appear in any patch revisions of 1.8.x.",
