						"displayName": "kosso",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/London"
					},
					"body": "Thanks for the update Stephen. I'm sure I've seen some apps do this, particularly in a popover. Now I need to see if I can remember which ones, to provide as an example. ;)\r\n",
