						"displayName": "kosso",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/London"
					},
					"body": "Which SDK branch/tag should this work from? \r\n\r\nI just built the latest 1.8.0.1 RC2 SDK (though appears as 1.9.0) from Github and tested this on an iPad with iOS 5.0.1 and both test pull up a modal/fullscreen camera. \r\n\r\nThx.",
