					"body": "Since the latest commit to master, I can confirm it works - in part. (Thank you!)\r\n\r\nHowever, using/defining a popoverView and arrowDirection leads to unexpected results. Also much oddness and size changing on orientation changes after settings these arguments too. \r\n\r\nI will follow up on this thread with findings and sample code - tomorrow.",
